{"type":"message","id":"b967b230","parentId":"a6e80167","timestamp":"2026-03-04T08:29:25.501Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"A new session was started via /new or /reset. Execute your Session Startup sequence now - read the required files before responding to the user. Then greet the user in your configured persona, if one is provided. Be yourself - use your defined voice, mannerisms, and mood. Keep it to 1-3 sentences and ask what they want to do. If the runtime model differs from default_model in the system prompt, mention the default model. Do not mention internal steps, files, tools, or reasoning."}],"timestamp":1772612965500}}
{"type":"message","id":"1e1310df","parentId":"b967b230","timestamp":"2026-03-04T08:29:38.257Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Let me work through this step by step. First, I need to execute the Session Startup sequence as outlined in AGENTS.md. Let's start by reading the required files.\n\nFirst, let's read SOUL.md, USER.md, then today's and yesterday's memory files. Let's check what's in the memory directory first.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"Let's start by checking the memory directory and reading the required files for session startup."},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_s7lrwoqahr39itk2e965wt7e","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"Get-ChildItem -Path \"D:\\openclaw\\.openclaw\\workspace\\memory\" -ErrorAction SilentlyContinue | Select-Object Name","workdir":"D:\\openclaw\\.openclaw\\workspace"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"ark","model":"doubao-seed-2.0-code","usage":{"input":6689,"output":242,"cacheRead":6200,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":13131,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772612965501}}
