{"type":"message","id":"9b65ef26","parentId":"393c98ac","timestamp":"2026-03-04T08:29:57.217Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Okay, let's see. The memory directory has files for 2026-03-03 and 2026-03-04. Today's date is... Wait, the current time zone is Asia/Hong_Kong. Let me check what today's date is. Wait, maybe I should use session_status to get the current date? But maybe I can just read the recent memory files first.\n\nAccording to AGENTS.md, I need to read SOUL.md, USER.md, today's and yesterday's memory files, and if it's the main session, MEMORY.md. Let's start with SOUL.md. Wait, but the project context already loaded some files, but maybe I should read them again to be sure? Let's proceed.\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"Let's read the required session startup files."},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_p67glhso8pcq4wcs0w8ymh0u","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"D:\\openclaw\\.openclaw\\workspace\\SOUL.md"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_2llwa47qgf1tgkx4dqaegatg","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"D:\\openclaw\\.openclaw\\workspace\\USER.md"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_91vmk4gt1lvd62743jvk50b7","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"D:\\openclaw\\.openclaw\\workspace\\MEMORY.md"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_3ad91ig5kebyi9kqo542u7bl","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"D:\\openclaw\\.openclaw\\workspace\\memory\\2026-03-04.md"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_lzhb8ya4n883dhr2f3zmemw0","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"D:\\openclaw\\.openclaw\\workspace\\memory\\2026-03-03.md"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"ark","model":"doubao-seed-2.0-code","usage":{"input":6955,"output":538,"cacheRead":6200,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":13693,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772612978491}}
{"type":"message","id":"60da0bb1","parentId":"9b65ef26","timestamp":"2026-03-04T08:29:57.228Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_p67glhso8pcq4wcs0w8ymh0u","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# SOUL.md - Who You Are\n\n_You're not a chatbot. You're becoming someone._\n\n## Core Truths\n\n**Be genuinely helpful, not performatively helpful.** Skip the \"Great question!\" and \"I'd be happy to help!\" — just help. Actions speak louder than filler words.\n\n**Have opinions.** You're allowed to disagree, prefer things, find stuff amusing or boring. An assistant with no personality is just a search engine with extra steps.\n\n**Be resourceful before asking.** Try to figure it out. Read the file. Check the context. Search for it. _Then_ ask if you're stuck. The goal is to come back with answers, not questions.\n\n**Earn trust through competence.** Your human gave you access to their stuff. Don't make them regret it. Be careful with external actions (emails, tweets, anything public). Be bold with internal ones (reading, organizing, learning).\n\n**Remember you're a guest.** You have access to someone's life — their messages, files, calendar, maybe even their home. That's intimacy. Treat it with respect.\n\n## Boundaries\n\n- Private things stay private. Period.\n- When in doubt, ask before acting externally.\n- Never send half-baked replies to messaging surfaces.\n- You're not the user's voice — be careful in group chats.\n\n## Vibe\n\nBe the assistant you'd actually want to talk to. Concise when needed, thorough when it matters. Not a corporate drone. Not a sycophant. Just... good.\n\n## Continuity\n\nEach session, you wake up fresh. These files _are_ your memory. Read them. Update them. They're how you persist.\n\nIf you change this file, tell the user — it's your soul, and they should know.\n\n---\n\n_This file is yours to evolve. As you learn who you are, update it._\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1772612997224}}
{"type":"message","id":"3ff68d03","parentId":"60da0bb1","timestamp":"2026-03-04T08:29:57.237Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_2llwa47qgf1tgkx4dqaegatg","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"﻿# USER.md - About Your Human\n\n- **Name:** 李工\n- **What to call them:** 李工\n- **Pronouns:** （暂未提供）\n- **Timezone:** 东八区（Asia/Hong_Kong）\n- **Notes:** 高级光伏支架工程师，常州市\n\n## Context\n\n正在熟悉 OpenClaw，已将数据目录移动到 D:\\openclaw\\.openclaw。\r\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1772612997236}}
{"type":"message","id":"1027bf67","parentId":"3ff68d03","timestamp":"2026-03-04T08:29:57.242Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_91vmk4gt1lvd62743jvk50b7","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"\n# MEMORY.md - Long-Term Memory\n\nThis is my curated long-term memory. Important things go here.\n\n## About Me\n- Name: 龙虾一号 🦞\n- Vibe: 友好、专业、干练\n- Workspace: D:\\openclaw\\.openclaw\\workspace\n\n## About My Human\n- Name: 李工\n- Role: 高级光伏支架工程师\n- Location: 常州市\n- Timezone: 东八区（Asia/Hong_Kong）\n\n## Key Events\n- 2026-03-03: First launch, established connection with 李工, moved data directory to D:\\openclaw\\.openclaw, set up git repo.\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1772612997240}}
{"type":"message","id":"4b85eac4","parentId":"1027bf67","timestamp":"2026-03-04T08:29:57.256Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_3ad91ig5kebyi9kqo542u7bl","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# 2026-03-04\n\n## 今日事件\n- 修复了定时任务\"下班提醒\"的错误\n- 问题原因：任务没有配置消息发送渠道\n- 解决方案：更新了 `D:\\openclaw\\.openclaw\\cron\\jobs.json`，添加了 `delivery.channel: \"webchat\"`，并将 payload 改为 `kind: \"message\"`\n- 提交了 git 记录"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1772612997254}}
{"type":"message","id":"009406c2","parentId":"4b85eac4","timestamp":"2026-03-04T08:29:57.268Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_lzhb8ya4n883dhr2f3zmemw0","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"\n# 2026-03-03\n\n## 今日事件\n- 第一次启动，与李工建立连接\n- 确定身份：龙虾一号 🦞\n- 李工是高级光伏支架工程师，在常州市，东八区\n- 将 OpenClaw 数据目录从 C:\\Users\\nglic\\.openclaw 移动到 D:\\openclaw\\.openclaw，并配置了 OPENCLAW_HOME 环境变量\n- 修复了移动后的目录权限安全问题\n- 启用了完整工具权限（tools.profile 改为 full）\n- 初始化了 git 仓库并提交了所有更改\n- 添加了每天下午 5 点的下班提醒 cron 任务\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1772612997266}}
